<p>安装后检查docker是否安装成功</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span>docker version
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>将当前用户加入docker用户组</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">sudo </span>usermod <span class="nt">-aG</span> docker <span class="nv">$USER</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
